<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bevollmächtigt Hans Stetzman und Konrad Pilsacher, Diener des Rats, zur Vertretung beim Landgericht zu Hirschberg wegen aller darin liegenden Nürnberger Güter.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_97" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_97_r2l3">Wir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><ab facs="#facs_97_r2l2">gemeinlıch </ab></del></add> deʒ Rats der Stat cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l4"><expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> brief / vmb ſöliche ladung vnd klage / als hans <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l5">in der Grafſchaft cʒü <expan>Hirſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_97_r1l1">auf die </ab><ab facs="#facs_97_r1l2"><expan>Lantſchran<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_97_r1l3">cʒü <expan>hirſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab></add> / geladen hat vnd klagt hincʒ allen den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l6">güten vnd der habe / die wir die <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> gemeinklıch des Rats vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l7">auch <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / in der Grafſchaft cʒü <expan>Hirſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ligend </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l8"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ vvir Conraden pillſacher vnd Hanſen Stecʒman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">geben haben </del> gancʒen vnd vollen gewalt geben <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l11">auch den mit <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> briefe / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_97_r2l10">vns vnſere güte vnd habe </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat / vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l13">
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat 
<add><ab facs="#facs_97_r2l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">gemeinlich </del></ab></add> cʒü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></del> / cʒü verantwurten vnd cʒü <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tret<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l14">cʒü gewinne vnd cʒü verluſt vnd cʒü <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten / Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> <expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Ambroſij . x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_97" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> dez rats der
                                                stat czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> brief umb söliche
                                                ladung und klage, als Hans
                                                  <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> in der
                                                grafschaft czü <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                                  <add>auf die <expan>lantschran<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                  czü <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan></add> geladen
                                                hat und klagt hincz allen den güten und der habe,
                                                die wir, die <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                                gemeinklich des rats und auch
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czü
                                                  <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, in der
                                                grafschaft czü <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                                                ligend <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; daz wir
                                                Conraden Pillsacher und Hansen Steczman,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern, ganczen
                                                und vollen gewalt geben
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in auch den mit
                                                  <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> briefe <add>uns,
                                                  unsere güte und habe</add> czü verantwurten und
                                                czü <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tret<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, czü
                                                gewinne und czü verlust und czü
                                                  <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten. Mit
                                                  <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Ambrosii x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
